    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends 👋, Welcome To aGuideHub!  To disable ripple mui slider in react js, you can use  in slider. it will disable ripple mui slider in React JS. Today, I…","html":"<p>Hi Friends 👋,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! </p>\n<p>To disable ripple mui slider in react js, you can use <code class=\"language-text\">\"&amp;:hover, &amp;.Mui-focusVisible, &amp;.Mui-active\": { boxShadow: \"none\"}</code> in slider. it will disable ripple mui slider in React JS.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, How to disable ripple mui slider in react js</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Install the following packages to use mui slider in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npm install @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">yarn add @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install MUI and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import Material-UI slider.</li>\n<li>Use the slider Component</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Step 1: Install MUI and create a new React app.</h3>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Import Material-UI slider.</h3>\n<p>After installing <code class=\"language-text\">MUI</code>, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following line to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Box <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/Box\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Slider <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/Slider\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Use the slider Component.</h3>\n<p>Sliders reflect a range of values along a bar, from which users may select a single value. They are ideal for adjusting settings such as volume, brightness, or applying image filters.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Slider\n  aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Temperature\"</span>\n  defaultValue<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  getAriaValueText<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>valuetext<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    sx<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"&amp; .MuiSlider-thumb\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"&amp;:before\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token literal-property property\">boxShadow</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)\"</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"&amp;:hover, &amp;.Mui-focusVisible, &amp;.Mui-active\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token literal-property property\">boxShadow</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"none\"</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>MUI material disable ripple mui slider example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example, you need to import <code class=\"language-text\">slider</code> Component. Then, you can use you can use <code class=\"language-text\">\"&amp;:hover, &amp;.Mui-focusVisible, &amp;.Mui-active\": { boxShadow: \"none\"}</code> in slider . Then it will disable ripple mui slider in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Box <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/Box\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Slider <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@mui/material/Slider\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">valuetext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>value<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">°C</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">ColorSlider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Box sx<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">300</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Slider\n        aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>label<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Temperature\"</span>\n        defaultValue<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        getAriaValueText<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>valuetext<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        sx<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"&amp; .MuiSlider-thumb\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">24</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n            <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"&amp;:before\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              <span class=\"token literal-property property\">boxShadow</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)\"</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token string-property property\">\"&amp;:hover, &amp;.Mui-focusVisible, &amp;.Mui-active\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              <span class=\"token literal-property property\">boxShadow</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"none\"</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Box<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">@mui/material</code> component and disable ripple mui slider in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 320px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6f2c4ba276d77bf40651a37d90b84db9/4c812/disable-ripple.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.86075949367089%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRloAAABXRUJQVlA4IE4AAACwAwCdASoUAAwAPtFWpEuoJKOhsAgBABoJQBOj+ABgbLqU0c6tAADLT8EvBVrPbrARYOZcHQ9ik5Uhzeq4sgEnj+ZyPWOWZx2Ndt+RoAA='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, disable, ripple\"\n        title=\"React, disable, ripple\"\n        src=\"/static/6f2c4ba276d77bf40651a37d90b84db9/4c812/disable-ripple.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6f2c4ba276d77bf40651a37d90b84db9/81b7c/disable-ripple.webp 158w,\n/static/6f2c4ba276d77bf40651a37d90b84db9/6ea66/disable-ripple.webp 315w,\n/static/6f2c4ba276d77bf40651a37d90b84db9/4c812/disable-ripple.webp 320w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Here, we are provided code sandbox links for the above program disable ripple mui slider in react js. Then you can use whenever you want and do the changes as per your requirements.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aguidehub.com/codesandbox/?code=festive-mccarthy-qgcwmw\" rel=\"nofollow\"  target=\"_BLANK\" >Try it Yourself</a></p>\n<p>All the best 👍</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to disable ripple mui slider in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"September 24, 2023","description":"Example of disable ripple mui slider in React js with step by step tutorial - aGuideHub","social_image":"media/template/reactjs.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to hide thumb of mui slider in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2023-09-25-how-to-hide-thumb-of-mui-slider-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to create mui slider with icon in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2023-09-22-how-to-create-mui-slider-with-icon-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2023-09-24-how-to-disable-ripple-mui-slider-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2023-09-25-how-to-hide-thumb-of-mui-slider-in-react-js/","nextSlug":"/blog/2023-09-22-how-t